he ability of one player’s Butcher will trigger, causing each opponent to sacrifice a creature. That sacrifice causes the ability of the other player’s Butcher to trigger, and so on.','B',NULL,'0.13','0.44','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'B',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'マラキールの解体者',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'クリーチャー ― 吸血鬼・戦士',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'飛行マラキールの解体者かあなたがコントロールする他のクリーチャーが１体死亡するたび、各対戦相手はクリーチャーを１体生け贄に捧げる。',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'#_彼の判決は常に有罪だ。彼の量刑は常に死刑だ。_#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('368520','Child of Night','SVT','Creature — Vampire','C','{1}{B}','2','2','1',NULL,'Lifelink #_(Damage dealt by this creature also causes you to gain that much life.)_#','#_Sins that would be too gruesome in the light of day are made more pleasing in the dark of night._#',NULL,'Ash Wood','5','2.737',NULL,'B',NULL,'0.05','0.16','2.08',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'B',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'夜の子',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'クリーチャー ― 吸血鬼',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'絆魂（このクリーチャーがダメージを与える場合、さらにあなたはその点数分のライフを得る。）',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'#_陽の光の下ではあまりに陰惨な罪も、夜の闇の下ではより喜ばしい。_#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('368533','Coal Stoker','SVT','Creature — Elemental','C','{3}{R}','4','3','3',NULL,'When Coal Stoker enters the battlefield, if you cast it from your hand, add {R}{R}{R}.','#_"The day is mine! I sent three such creatures against my foe, then watched as my magefire popped her soldiers like overripe spleenfruits."£—Dobruk the Unstable, pyromancer_#',NULL,'Mark Zug','49','3.5','£1/25/2011: You get the mana whether you want it or not. If you don’t spend it, it will disappear at the end of the current step (or phase).£9/20/2013: If a creature (such as Clone) enters the battlefield as a copy of this creature, the copy’s “enters-the-battlefield” ability will still trigger as long as yo